{{MIint|exit\n|county=Macomb\n|cspan=15\n|location_special=[[Eastpointe, Michigan|Eastpointe]]\u2013[[St. Clair Shores, Michigan|St. Clair Shores]] city line\n|mile=226.893\n|exit=227\n|road=9 Mile Road\n|notes=}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|location_special=[[Eastpointe, Michigan|Eastpointe]]\u2013[[Roseville, Michigan|Roseville]]\u2013[[St. Clair Shores, Michigan|St. Clair Shores]] city tripoint\n|mile=227.967\n|exit=228\n|road=10 Mile Road\n|notes=}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|location_special=[[Roseville, Michigan|Roseville]]\u2013[[St. Clair Shores, Michigan|St. Clair Shores]] city line\n|lspan=2\n|mile=228.742\n|mile2=229.426\n|exit=229\n|road={{jct|state=MI|I|696|dir1=west|city1=Lansing}}<br />11&nbsp;Mile Road\n|notes=Eastern terminus of I-696}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|mile=230.014\n|exit=230\n|road=12&nbsp;Mile Road\n|notes=}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|location =Roseville\n|lspan=2\n|mile=230.890\n|exit=231\n|type=incomplete\n|road={{jct|state=MI|M|3|name1=Gratiot Avenue}}\n|notes=Eastbound exit to northbound M-3 and westbound entrance only}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|mile=231.354\n|exit=232\n|road=Little Mack Avenue\n|notes=}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|location =Clinton Township\n|ctdab=Macomb\n|mile=234.209\n|exit=234\n|road=Harper Avenue\n|notes=Signed as exits 234A (south) and 234B (north)}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|location =Harrison Township\n|lspan=2\n|mile=234.873\n|exit=235\n|type=incomplete\n|road=Shook Road\n|notes=Westbound exit and eastbound entrance}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|mile=235.909\n|mile2=235.921\n|exit=236\n|road=[[Metropolitan Parkway (Detroit area)|Metropolitan Parkway]]\n|notes=}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|location =Mt. Clemens\n|mile=237.266\n|exit=237\n|road=North River Road&nbsp;\u2013 [[Mt. Clemens, Michigan|Mt. Clemens]]\n|notes=}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|location_special=[[Harrison Township, Michigan|Harrison]]\u2013[[Chesterfield Township, Michigan|Chesterfield]] township line\n|mile=240.027\n|mile2=240.259\n|exit=240\n|road={{jct|state=MI|M|59|location1=[[Selfridge Air National Guard Base|Selfridge ANGB]]|city2=Utica}}\n|notes=Signed as exits 240A (east) and 240B (west) eastbound; eastern terminus of M-59; roadway continues beyond terminus as William P. Rosso Highway}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|location =Chesterfield Township\n|lspan=3\n|mile=241.193\n|exit=241\n|road=21 Mile Road\n|notes=}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|mile=243.453\n|exit=243\n|road={{jct|state=MI|M|3|dir1=south|city1=Utica}}<br/>{{jct|state=MI|M|29|city1=Algonac|city2=New Baltimore|dir1=north}}\n|notes=Northern terminus of M-3; southern terminus of M-29; signs eastbound omit M-3 and Utica; signs westbound omit Algonac}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|mile=246.737\n|exit=247\n|type=incomplete\n|road={{jct|state=MI|M|19|city1=Richmond|city2=New Haven|dir1=north}}\n|notes=Eastbound exit and westbound entrance; southern terminus of M-19}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|location =Lenox Township\n|mile=248.118\n|exit=248\n|road=26&nbsp;Mile Road&nbsp;\u2013 [[Marine City, Michigan|Marine City]]\n|notes=Westbound access to New Haven}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|county=St. Clair\n|cspan=9\n|location_special=[[Casco Township, St. Clair County, Michigan|Casco]]\u2013[[Columbus Township, St. Clair County, Michigan|Columbus]] township line\n|mile=257.185\n|exit=257\n|road=[[Richmond, Michigan|Richmond]], [[St. Clair, Michigan|St. Clair]]\n|notes=Signs eastbound omit Richmond}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|location =St. Clair Township\n|mile=262.131\n|exit=262\n|road=Wadhams Road\n|notes=}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|location =Kimball Township\n|mile=266.330\n|exit=266\n|road={{jct|state=MI|BL|94|dir1=east|dab1=Port Huron|name1=Gratiot Road|city1=Marysville}}\n|notes=Signs westbound omit BL I-94; western terminus of BL I-94}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|location_special=[[Kimball Township, Michigan|Kimball]]\u2013[[Port Huron Township, Michigan|Port Huron]] township line\n|mile=269.525\n|exit=269\n|road=Range Road, Dove Street\n|notes=Signs westbound omit Dove Street}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|location =Port Huron Township\n|lspan=3\n|mile=271.271\n|mile2=271.820\n|exit=271\n|espan=2\n|type=concur\n|road={{jct|state=MI|I|69|dir1=west|city1=Flint|city2=Lansing}}\n|notes=Western end of I-69 concurrency; signs eastbound omit Lansing; exit 198 on I-69}}\n{{MIint\n|mile=271.529\n|exit=271\n|type=incomplete\n|road={{jct|state=MI|BL|69|dab1=Port Huron|dir1=east|city1=Port Huron}}\n|notes=Eastbound exit and westbound entrance; western terminus of BL I-69}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|mile=273.826\n|exit=274\n|road=Water Street, Lapeer Avenue&nbsp;\u2013 [[Port Huron, Michigan|Port Huron]]\n|notes=Signed as 274A (Lapeer Avenue) and 274B (Water Street) eastbound; indirect access to Lapeer Avenue via Lapeer Connector (former [[M-146 (Michigan highway)|M-146]]); no direct eastbound entrance to Blue Water Bridge}}\n{{MIint|exit\n|mile=275.102\n|exit=275\n|location =Port Huron\n|lspan=2\n|road={{jct|state=MI|BL|69|dab1=Port Huron|dir1=west|BL|94|dab2=Port Huron|dir2=west|M|25|Tour|LHCT|name3=Pine Grove Avenue|city1=Downtown Port Huron}}\n|notes= Eastbound last exit before Canada; eastern terminus of BL I-69/BL I-94; southern terminus of M-25; signs eastbound omit BL I-69/BL I-94; no exit number westbound}}\n{{jctbridge|exit\n|mile=274.770\n|place=Toll Plaza (eastbound)<br/>U.S. Customs (westbound)}}\n{{jctbridge|exit\n|river=[[St. Clair River]]\n|lspan=2\n|type=toll\n|mile=275.304\n|mile2=275.398\n|mspan=2\n|bridge=[[Blue Water Bridge]] (tolled)}}\n{{jctint|exit\n|mile=none\n|road={{jct|province=ON|ON|402|Tour|LHCT|dir1=east|city1=Sarnia|city2=London}}\n|notes=Continuation into Ontario}}\n{{jctbtm|exit|keys=closed,concur,incomplete,toll}}\n\n==Related trunklines==\n{{main|Interstate 194 (Michigan)|Business routes of Interstate 94 in Michigan|l1=Interstate 194}}\n[[File:Interstate 194 Michigan.jpg|thumb|Signage along I-194/M-66, the \"Sojourner Truth Downtown Parkway\"]]\nThere are nine highways related to I-94 in Michigan. The first is the spur into downtown [[Battle Creek, Michigan|Battle Creek]] numbered I-194 and nicknamed \"The Penetrator\"<ref name=\"enq\">{{cite news |last = Vander Meer |first = John J. |title = Penetrator to Get $1.6M Face-Lift |url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21789177/penetrator_to_get_16m_facelift/ |work = [[Battle Creek Enquirer]] |date = March 18, 2002 |pages = 1A, [https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21789198/penetrator_to_get_16m_facelift_part/ 7A] |oclc = 33956507 |access-date = July 12, 2018 |via = Newspapers.com }} </ref> and officially called the \"Sojourner Truth Downtown Parkway\".<ref name=\"barnett\">{{harvp|Barnett|2004|p=201}}.</ref> This [[List of auxiliary Interstate Highways|auxiliary Interstate Highway]] runs for about {{convert|3|mi|km|spell=in}} to connect I-94 northward into downtown. The other eight highways are [[business loop]]s of I-94 that connect various cities' downtowns with the main freeway. Unlike I-194, these loops are not freeways. Located from west to east along I-94's routing in Michigan, they serve [[Interstate 94 Business (Benton Harbor, Michigan)|Benton Harbor\u2013St. Joseph]], [[Interstate 94 Business (Kalamazoo, Michigan)|Kalamazoo]], [[Interstate 94 Business (Battle Creek, Michigan)|Battle Creek]], [[Interstate 94 Business (Marshall, Michigan)|Marshall]], [[Interstate 94 Business (Albion, Michigan)|Albion]], [[Interstate 94 Business (Jackson, Michigan)|Jackson]], [[Interstate 94 Business (Ann Arbor, Michigan)|Ann Arbor]], and [[Interstate 94 Business (Port Huron, Michigan)|Port Huron]].<ref name=MDOT13/>\n{{Clear}}\n\n==See also==\n*{{portal-inline|Michigan Highways}}\n\n==Notes==\n{{reflist|group=lower-alpha}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Interstate 94 in Michigan}}\n{{AttachedKML|display=title,inline}}\n*{{osmrelation-inline|104454|I-94 in Michigan}}\n*[http://www.michiganhighways.org/listings/I-094.html I-94] at Michigan Highways\n*[http://www.michiganhighways.org/listings/M-112.html M-112] at Michigan Highways\n*[http://www.michiganhighways.org/indepth/early_I-94.html Early Willow Run, Detroit Industrial & Edsel Ford Expressways] at Michigan Highways\n\n{{state 